bilingual.source: Have you got a new sweater, Sam?

list.abstract: sweater（英 [ˈswetə(r)]，美 [ˈswetər]），英语单词，名词，意思为针织套衫（美式英语）；〈旧〉榨取雇员血汗的雇主。短语搭配有Siwash sweater（厚毛线衣），例句为“It used to be my mum's sweater.（它以前是我妈妈的毛衣。）” sweater名词类近义词有jersey、sports shirt，复数形式为sweaters。

yingyinNormal.en: I didn't bring a sweater. Then, we should really go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我没有带毛衣来。那么我们最好赶快走。

yingyinNormal.en: You own the damn thing. Just take a freaking sweater!
yingyinNormal.zh: 还不都你说了算，痛快拿件毛衣就行了！

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. My sweater. I've been looking for this for like a month.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的毛衣，我找这件毛衣找了一个月。

yingyinNormal.en: I mean, first it's my jewelry. And if it's not my jewelry, it's my blue sweater. And if it's not my sweater, it's my sunglasses.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先是我的首饰，不是首饰，就是我的蓝色毛衣，不是蓝色毛衣，就是我的太阳眼镜。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, I wore that cashmere sweater on a date last night. Oh?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我昨晚穿那件喀什米尔毛衣去约会。哦？

yingyinNormal.en: All right. You've paid for a sweater, and you're in Sheldon Square.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你买了件毛衣，现在你在谢尔顿广场。

yingyinNormal.en: Really? This time of year? It's a bit nippy. Then, put on a sweater.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是吗？这个季节吗？那可有点冷。那就穿件毛衣。

yingyinNormal.en: She's telling the truth. I bought the sweater for my daughter, for her birthday.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她说的是实话，我给我女儿买了毛衣，为了她的生日。

yingyinNormal.en: Mom, Chandler was just saying how beautiful your sweater is. Oh, thank you Chandler. I just bought it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈，钱德说你的毛衣很好看。谢谢你，这是新衣服。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry. Rachel, we should probably go. I ran out of diapers, and I had to use your sweater.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很抱歉，瑞秋，我们该走了。尿片用完了，我得用你的毛衣代替。

yingyinNormal.en: What'd you get? Oh well, all right, I got, thank you, I got, this, you know "I want a job" sweater. Oh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们买了什么？我买了，谢谢，我买了这件“我要工作”毛衣。

yingyinNormal.en: Suppose I could run downtown and pick up something at Shel Mart. Yeah, whatever. Just go buy a sweater.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那我可以去市中心的谢尔玛买一件。随便啊，去买件毛衣就是了。

yingyinNormal.en: Why? Because I got an ugly, itchy sweater, and my brother got a car? No,I was her favorite.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了？就因为她送我件又丑又扎人的毛衣，而却送我哥辆车？才不是呢，她最喜欢我了。

yingyinNormal.en: Models in my diner! Oh, no. I wore the wrong sweater vest. You also wore the wrong face, body, and personality.
yingyinNormal.zh: 模特来我的餐厅里！惨了，今天穿这件毛衣是错的。你的那张脸，身材与个性也都是错的。

yingyinNormal.en: And I got him this amazing autographed copy of the Feynman lectures on physics. Nice. I got him a sweater.
yingyinNormal.zh: 而我送给他这份完美的，有费曼亲笔签名的关于物理学演讲的拷贝。太棒了，我要送他一件毛衣。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, listen, how cold is it going to be there? Do I need a coat or will all these sweater vests be enough? What? I love you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好了，不过那边会有多冷？我要带外套，还是带这些毛衣就够了？怎么了？ 我爱你。

yingyinNormal.en: You were her roommate. How do you not have a single nice story about her? She took my white sweater and returned it pink.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是她室友，你连她的一件好事都说不出吗？她向我借了件白毛衣，还回来就成粉红色了。

yingyinNormal.en: And I'd just like to point out that even though the sweater was uncomfortable, I didn't use it as an excuse to antagonize everyone around me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我必须说，虽然这毛衣穿上去不太舒服，我可没有拿它作为与所有人为敌的借口。

yingyinNormal.en: That's a nice sweater vest.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这件毛线背心不错。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm wearing a cable knit sweater! I'm I'm wearing slacks! You turned me into you!
yingyinNormal.zh: 我现在都穿针织毛衫了！我，我还穿着宽松的裤子！你把我变成了你！
